dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Shows "Deg. west from London" and "Hours west from London." Decorative title cartouche depicting a cliff, waterfall, and natives. Later copy lacking Jeffery's name below title. 1 map: hand col.; 18 x 22 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
